WEBVTT

00:08:28.720 --> 00:08:31.256
and she said, "Three dollars."

00:08:31.280 --> 00:08:35.135
(Laughter)

00:08:35.159 --> 00:08:38.256
I said that seemed a bit high
for one cookie.

00:08:38.280 --> 00:08:40.015
(Laughter)

00:08:40.039 --> 00:08:41.240
It was small.

00:08:43.320 --> 00:08:46.016
"I know," she acknowledged with a grin,

00:08:46.040 --> 00:08:47.440
"but I'm worth it."

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:50.896
And therein lie the words of wisdom

00:08:50.920 --> 00:08:55.400
of a young girl whose brief life
forever impacted mine.

00:08:56.800 --> 00:08:58.240
Crystal was worth it,

00:08:59.080 --> 00:09:04.376
and shouldn't every child whose life
is shortened by a horrific illness